# Q2 Threat Outlook (intentionally bad)

## Executive summary

We assess that Volt Typhoon will continue prepositioning in U.S. critical-infrastructure networks through Q3.

## Analysis

Volt Typhoon targeted the regional utility in April. "The actor maintains long-term persistence through valid accounts and built-in tools."

We assess with high confidence, based on a single vendor advisory, that exploitation of CVE-2026-0001 will accelerate over the next 60 days.

## Recommendations

The group will pivot to financial services in Q3.
